  ${
    $d r s t x J $.  $d r s t x S $.  $d r s t x X $.
    opnfbas.1 $e |- X = U. J $.
    $( The collection of open supersets of a nonempty set in a topology is a
       neighborhoods of the set, one of the motivations for the filter
       concept.  (Contributed by Jeff Hankins, 2-Sep-2009.) $)
    opnfbas $p |- ( ( J e. Top /\ S C_ X /\ S =/= (/) ) -> { x e. J | S C_ x }
        e.
  fBas ) $=
